      *    *===========================================================*
      *    * Work per subroutines di Det                               *
      *    *-----------------------------------------------------------*
       01  w-det.
      *        *-------------------------------------------------------*
      *        * Work per Det se presenti dipendenze per il cliente    *
      *        * commerciale                                           *
      *        *-------------------------------------------------------*
           05  w-det-___-___.
      *            *---------------------------------------------------*
      *            * Esito della determinazione                        *
      *            * - S : Si, il cliente   commerciale ha dipendenze  *
      *            * - N : No, il cliente   commerciale non ha dipen-  *
      *            *       denze                                       *
      *            *---------------------------------------------------*
               10  w-det-___-___-snx      pic  x(01)                  .
      *            *---------------------------------------------------*
      *            * Codice cliente commerciale                        *
      *            *---------------------------------------------------*
               10  w-det-___-___-cli      pic  9(07)                  .
      *            *---------------------------------------------------*
      *            * Contatore dipendenze rilevate                     *
      *            *---------------------------------------------------*
               10  w-det-___-___-ctr      pic  9(05)                  .
      *            *---------------------------------------------------*
      *            * Codice dipendenza, solo se unica per il cliente   *
      *            *---------------------------------------------------*
               10  w-det-___-___-dpz      pic  x(04)                  .


           move      w-tes-cod-arc (1)    to   w-det-___-___-cli      .
           perform   det-___-___-000      thru det-___-___-999        .
           move      w-det-___-___-snx    to   w-tes-cod-arc-snd (1)  .





      *    *===========================================================*
      *    * Determinazione se presenti dipendenze per il cliente      *
      *    * commerciale                                               *
      *    *-----------------------------------------------------------*
       det-___-___-000.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Normalizzazione flag di esito                   *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      "N"                  to   w-det-___-___-snx      .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Normalizzazione codice dipendenza unica         *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      spaces               to   w-det-___-___-dpz      .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Normalizzazione contatore                       *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      zero                 to   w-det-___-___-ctr      .
       det-___-___-100.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Start su file [___]                             *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      "SK"                 to   f-ope                  .
           move      "NL"                 to   f-cfr                  .
           move      "CODCLI    "         to   f-key                  .
           move      w-det-___-___-cli    to   rf-___-cod-cli         .
           move      spaces               to   rf-___-dpz-cli         .
           move      "pgm/___/fls/ioc/obj/iof___"
                                          to   s-pat                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mfiltp"
                                         using s                      .
           call      s-pat               using f
                                               rf-___                 .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Se Start errata : ad uscita                 *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        f-sts                not  = e-not-err
                     go to det-___-___-900.
       det-___-___-200.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Next su [___]                                   *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      "RN"                 to   f-ope                  .
           move      "pgm/___/fls/ioc/obj/iof___"
                                          to   s-pat                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mfiltp"
                                         using s                      .
           call      s-pat               using f
                                               rf-___                 .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Se 'at end' : ad uscita                     *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        f-sts                not  = e-not-err
                     go to det-___-___-900.
       det-___-___-300.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Max su [___], se non superato : ad uscita       *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        rf-___-cod-cli       not  = w-det-___-___-cli
                     go to det-___-___-900.
       det-___-___-400.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Selezioni su [___]                              *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        rf-___-dpz-cli       =    spaces
                     go to det-___-___-200.
       det-___-___-500.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Incremento contatore                            *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           add       1                    to   w-det-___-___-ctr      .
       det-___-___-600.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Bufferizzazioni                                 *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*













       det-___-___-800.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Riciclo a record [___] successivo               *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           go to     det-___-___-200.
       det-___-___-900.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Uscita                                          *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           go to     det-___-___-999.
       det-___-___-999.
           exit.

